Shujiro, pumunta kayo at tingnan
kung saan dinadala ang mga bangkay.

00:21:21.188 --> 00:21:22.021
Okay.

00:21:22.605 --> 00:21:24.271
Oh, at ikaw, Iroha.

00:21:25.105 --> 00:21:25.938
Dito.

